Ughelli â€“ Old students of Ovwian Secondary School, Ovwian (OSSO), Udu Local Government Area of Delta State, will on Saturday, December 14, 2019, hold their reunion/end of year party.
According to a statement signed by the president, Pastor Aaron Akpovofene, and Publicity Director, Sunday Apah, the event would hold at Reigns Hotel, Igbogidi Town, Udu LGA of Delta State by 12pm and would be chaired by the Delta State Commissioner for Special Duties, Henry Sakpra.
The statement urged all alma maters of OSSO to try and attend the reunion/end of year party for the upliftment of the school.